<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克非常吃惊，他沿着豆茎向上看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>向上！向上！向上！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>豆茎真的长到了天上！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那位老爷爷说的是真的，” 杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些豆子真的是魔豆！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克小心地爬上豆茎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬呀爬呀……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快就离地面非常非常远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇哦！”杰克大吃一惊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这根豆茎这么高！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克继续往上爬……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬过了云层。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他看到了一片神奇的土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克从豆茎上走下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是哪儿？”他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一边看，一边沿着小路往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克又累又饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，杰克看到了一个大房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门口站着一个女人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许她会给我一些吃的。” 杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好！”杰克礼貌地打招呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摸了摸肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很饿，您能给我一些吃的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃……”女人看起来很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周，然后又看了看杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想要一些吃的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克向前几步：“是的，求您了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我昨天没吃晚饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天也没吃早饭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人咬了咬嘴唇：“你还是快走吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的丈夫……”女人小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个食人魔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>